    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Chlaenius (Chlaeniostenus) silvai n. sp. (a) habitus, holotype male (dorsal view); (b) habitus, holotype male (ventral view); (c) and (d) median lobe of aedeagus, holotype male (lateral and dorsal views, respectively); (e) right and left parameres of aedeagus, holotype male (lateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10468223/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

