    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Chlaenius (Chlaeniostenus) kirschenhoferi n. sp. (a) habitus, holotype male (dorsal view); (b) habitus, holotype male (ventral view); (c) and (d) median lobe of aedeagus, holotype male (lateral and dorsal views, respectively); (e) right and left parameres of aedeagus, holotype male (lateral view)." ;
